Vendored client assets live here. Fetch on first build:

  curl -L https://unpkg.com/htmx.org@2.0.4/dist/htmx.min.js \
    -o htmx.min.js
  curl -L https://unpkg.com/htmx-ext-ws@2.0.3/ws.js \
    -o htmx-ext-ws.js
  curl -L https://unpkg.com/uplot@1.6.31/dist/uPlot.iife.min.js \
    -o uplot.min.js
  curl -L https://unpkg.com/uplot@1.6.31/dist/uPlot.min.css \
    -o uplot.min.css

Pin the versions in this file. CMake's install rule picks up
*.js / *.css in this directory.
